com.amazonaws.services.machinelearning.model

Class PredictRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.AmazonWebServiceRequest
      • com.amazonaws.services.machinelearning.model.PredictRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class PredictRequest
extends AmazonWebServiceRequest
implements Serializable
    Container for the parameters to the Predict operation.

    A realtime operation that generates prediction for the observation using given ML Model Id

    Note that not all response fields will be populated as this is dependent on the type of requested model

    See Also:
    AmazonMachineLearning.predict(PredictRequest), Serialized Form
